invalid type: string "This project strengthens understanding of JVM internals and prepares students for real-world debugging and \nperformance optimization challenges. \nThe innovation of the project lies in combining: \n\u{f0b7} Live memory monitoring \n\u{f0b7} Leak simulation \n\u{f0b7} Heap dump analysis \nThis makes the system educational, practical, and technically relevant. \n \n ", expecte